2019/05/14 21:02:09
select post_nick,t8.post_id,t9.cat_id,t8.cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from (select post_nick,t6.post_id,cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from(select t3.post_nick,t3.post_id,t3.cat_name,t3.post_title,t3.post_time,t3.reply_nick,t3.reply_time,t4.likes from (select t1.user_nick as post_nick,t1.post_id,t1.cat_name,t1.post_title,t1.pubtime as post_time,t2.user_nick as reply_nick,t2.max_pubtime as reply_time from (select user_nick,post_id,cat_name,post_title,pubtime from forum_post inner join user_data on forum_post.user_account = user_data.user_account) as t1 left join (select user_nick,post_id,max(pubtime) as max_pubtime from forum_comment inner join user_data on forum_comment.user_account = user_data.user_account group by post_id) as t2 on t1.post_id=t2.post_id) as t3 left join (select post_id,count(*) as likes from give_a_like group by post_id) as t4 on t3.post_id=t4.post_id) as t6 left join (select post_id,count(*) as reply_sum from (select post_id from forum_comment union all select post_id from forum_reply) as t5 group by post_id) as t7 on t6.post_id=t7.post_id) as t8 left join (select cat_id,cat_name from forum_cat) as t9 on t8.cat_name = t9.cat_name order by post_id desc limit 0,8
---------------------------------------

2019/05/14 21:33:04
select post_nick,t8.post_id,t9.cat_id,t8.cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from (select post_nick,t6.post_id,cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from(select t3.post_nick,t3.post_id,t3.cat_name,t3.post_title,t3.post_time,t3.reply_nick,t3.reply_time,t4.likes from (select t1.user_nick as post_nick,t1.post_id,t1.cat_name,t1.post_title,t1.pubtime as post_time,t2.user_nick as reply_nick,t2.max_pubtime as reply_time from (select user_nick,post_id,cat_name,post_title,pubtime from forum_post inner join user_data on forum_post.user_account = user_data.user_account) as t1 left join (select user_nick,post_id,max(pubtime) as max_pubtime from forum_comment inner join user_data on forum_comment.user_account = user_data.user_account group by post_id) as t2 on t1.post_id=t2.post_id) as t3 left join (select post_id,count(*) as likes from give_a_like group by post_id) as t4 on t3.post_id=t4.post_id) as t6 left join (select post_id,count(*) as reply_sum from (select post_id from forum_comment union all select post_id from forum_reply) as t5 group by post_id) as t7 on t6.post_id=t7.post_id) as t8 left join (select cat_id,cat_name from forum_cat) as t9 on t8.cat_name = t9.cat_name order by post_id desc limit 0,8
---------------------------------------

---------------------------------------

2019/05/14 21:35:50
select post_nick,t8.post_id,t9.cat_id,t8.cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from (select post_nick,t6.post_id,cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from(select t3.post_nick,t3.post_id,t3.cat_name,t3.post_title,t3.post_time,t3.reply_nick,t3.reply_time,t4.likes from (select t1.user_nick as post_nick,t1.post_id,t1.cat_name,t1.post_title,t1.pubtime as post_time,t2.user_nick as reply_nick,t2.max_pubtime as reply_time from (select user_nick,post_id,cat_name,post_title,pubtime from forum_post inner join user_data on forum_post.user_account = user_data.user_account) as t1 left join (select user_nick,post_id,max(pubtime) as max_pubtime from forum_comment inner join user_data on forum_comment.user_account = user_data.user_account group by post_id) as t2 on t1.post_id=t2.post_id) as t3 left join (select post_id,count(*) as likes from give_a_like group by post_id) as t4 on t3.post_id=t4.post_id) as t6 left join (select post_id,count(*) as reply_sum from (select post_id from forum_comment union all select post_id from forum_reply) as t5 group by post_id) as t7 on t6.post_id=t7.post_id) as t8 left join (select cat_id,cat_name from forum_cat) as t9 on t8.cat_name = t9.cat_name order by post_id desc limit 0,8
---------------------------------------

2019/05/14 21:40:16
select count(*) from forum_post
---------------------------------------

---------------------------------------
2019/05/14 21:40:16
select post_nick,t8.post_id,t9.cat_id,t8.cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from (select post_nick,t6.post_id,cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from(select t3.post_nick,t3.post_id,t3.cat_name,t3.post_title,t3.post_time,t3.reply_nick,t3.reply_time,t4.likes from (select t1.user_nick as post_nick,t1.post_id,t1.cat_name,t1.post_title,t1.pubtime as post_time,t2.user_nick as reply_nick,t2.max_pubtime as reply_time from (select user_nick,post_id,cat_name,post_title,pubtime from forum_post inner join user_data on forum_post.user_account = user_data.user_account) as t1 left join (select user_nick,post_id,max(pubtime) as max_pubtime from forum_comment inner join user_data on forum_comment.user_account = user_data.user_account group by post_id) as t2 on t1.post_id=t2.post_id) as t3 left join (select post_id,count(*) as likes from give_a_like group by post_id) as t4 on t3.post_id=t4.post_id) as t6 left join (select post_id,count(*) as reply_sum from (select post_id from forum_comment union all select post_id from forum_reply) as t5 group by post_id) as t7 on t6.post_id=t7.post_id) as t8 left join (select cat_id,cat_name from forum_cat) as t9 on t8.cat_name = t9.cat_name order by post_id desc limit 0,8
---------------------------------------

---------------------------------------
2019/05/14 21:40:16

2019/05/14 21:40:51
select count(*) from forum_post
---------------------------------------

2019/05/14 21:40:51
select post_nick,t8.post_id,t9.cat_id,t8.cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from (select post_nick,t6.post_id,cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from(select t3.post_nick,t3.post_id,t3.cat_name,t3.post_title,t3.post_time,t3.reply_nick,t3.reply_time,t4.likes from (select t1.user_nick as post_nick,t1.post_id,t1.cat_name,t1.post_title,t1.pubtime as post_time,t2.user_nick as reply_nick,t2.max_pubtime as reply_time from (select user_nick,post_id,cat_name,post_title,pubtime from forum_post inner join user_data on forum_post.user_account = user_data.user_account) as t1 left join (select user_nick,post_id,max(pubtime) as max_pubtime from forum_comment inner join user_data on forum_comment.user_account = user_data.user_account group by post_id) as t2 on t1.post_id=t2.post_id) as t3 left join (select post_id,count(*) as likes from give_a_like group by post_id) as t4 on t3.post_id=t4.post_id) as t6 left join (select post_id,count(*) as reply_sum from (select post_id from forum_comment union all select post_id from forum_reply) as t5 group by post_id) as t7 on t6.post_id=t7.post_id) as t8 left join (select cat_id,cat_name from forum_cat) as t9 on t8.cat_name = t9.cat_name order by post_id desc limit 0,8
---------------------------------------

---------------------------------------

select com_id,forum_reply.user_account,user_nick,content from forum_reply inner join user_data on forum_reply.user_account = user_data.user_account where post_id = 1 and floor_id = 1 order by com_id asc
---------------------------------------

---------------------------------------
2019/05/14 21:41:21
select cat_id,cat_name from forum_cat
---------------------------------------

---------------------------------------
2019/05/14 21:41:21
select user_nick,post_id,cat_name,post_title,pubtime from forum_post inner join user_data on forum_post.user_account = user_data.user_account where cat_name = '公告'
---------------------------------------

---------------------------------------
2019/05/14 21:41:21
select count(*) from forum_post
---------------------------------------

---------------------------------------
2019/05/14 21:41:21
select post_nick,t8.post_id,t9.cat_id,t8.cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from (select post_nick,t6.post_id,cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from(select t3.post_nick,t3.post_id,t3.cat_name,t3.post_title,t3.post_time,t3.reply_nick,t3.reply_time,t4.likes from (select t1.user_nick as post_nick,t1.post_id,t1.cat_name,t1.post_title,t1.pubtime as post_time,t2.user_nick as reply_nick,t2.max_pubtime as reply_time from (select user_nick,post_id,cat_name,post_title,pubtime from forum_post inner join user_data on forum_post.user_account = user_data.user_account) as t1 left join (select user_nick,post_id,max(pubtime) as max_pubtime from forum_comment inner join user_data on forum_comment.user_account = user_data.user_account group by post_id) as t2 on t1.post_id=t2.post_id) as t3 left join (select post_id,count(*) as likes from give_a_like group by post_id) as t4 on t3.post_id=t4.post_id) as t6 left join (select post_id,count(*) as reply_sum from (select post_id from forum_comment union all select post_id from forum_reply) as t5 group by post_id) as t7 on t6.post_id=t7.post_id) as t8 left join (select cat_id,cat_name from forum_cat) as t9 on t8.cat_name = t9.cat_name order by post_id desc limit 0,8
---------------------------------------

---------------------------------------

2019/05/14 21:46:12
select post_nick,t8.post_id,t9.cat_id,t8.cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from (select post_nick,t6.post_id,cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from(select t3.post_nick,t3.post_id,t3.cat_name,t3.post_title,t3.post_time,t3.reply_nick,t3.reply_time,t4.likes from (select t1.user_nick as post_nick,t1.post_id,t1.cat_name,t1.post_title,t1.pubtime as post_time,t2.user_nick as reply_nick,t2.max_pubtime as reply_time from (select user_nick,post_id,cat_name,post_title,pubtime from forum_post inner join user_data on forum_post.user_account = user_data.user_account) as t1 left join (select user_nick,post_id,max(pubtime) as max_pubtime from forum_comment inner join user_data on forum_comment.user_account = user_data.user_account group by post_id) as t2 on t1.post_id=t2.post_id) as t3 left join (select post_id,count(*) as likes from give_a_like group by post_id) as t4 on t3.post_id=t4.post_id) as t6 left join (select post_id,count(*) as reply_sum from (select post_id from forum_comment union all select post_id from forum_reply) as t5 group by post_id) as t7 on t6.post_id=t7.post_id) as t8 left join (select cat_id,cat_name from forum_cat) as t9 on t8.cat_name = t9.cat_name order by post_id desc limit 0,8
---------------------------------------

2019/05/14 22:07:08
select count(*) from forum_post
---------------------------------------

---------------------------------------
2019/05/14 22:07:08
select post_nick,t8.post_id,t9.cat_id,t8.cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from (select post_nick,t6.post_id,cat_name,post_title,post_time,reply_nick,reply_time,likes,reply_sum from(select t3.post_nick,t3.post_id,t3.cat_name,t3.post_title,t3.post_time,t3.reply_nick,t3.reply_time,t4.likes from (select t1.user_nick as post_nick,t1.post_id,t1.cat_name,t1.post_title,t1.pubtime as post_time,t2.user_nick as reply_nick,t2.max_pubtime as reply_time from (select user_nick,post_id,cat_name,post_title,pubtime from forum_post inner join user_data on forum_post.user_account = user_data.user_account) as t1 left join (select user_nick,post_id,max(pubtime) as max_pubtime from forum_comment inner join user_data on forum_comment.user_account = user_data.user_account group by post_id) as t2 on t1.post_id=t2.post_id) as t3 left join (select post_id,count(*) as likes from give_a_like group by post_id) as t4 on t3.post_id=t4.post_id) as t6 left join (select post_id,count(*) as reply_sum from (select post_id from forum_comment union all select post_id from forum_reply) as t5 group by post_id) as t7 on t6.post_id=t7.post_id) as t8 left join (select cat_id,cat_name from forum_cat) as t9 on t8.cat_name = t9.cat_name order by post_id desc limit 0,8
---------------------------------------
